{"tid":734099,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[3322不再？]八成受訪校長同意檢視要求","createTime":"2018-07-08T10:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T14:24:34.000Z","uid":1788,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"85cdaab3dfa9c7452530e1bb835bcada8d987359","tid":734099,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:41:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>近八成受訪中學校長同意當局檢視入大學文憑試要求</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港中學校長會5至6月向全港125間中學的校長進行問卷調查，7成8受訪校長同意，教育局應檢視中學文憑試四個核心科目「3322」學士學位課程的最低入學要求。<br />\n<br />\n香港中學校長會主席李雪英指，2017年中學文憑試，考獲五科22分或以上成績的學生有8612人，當中有310人在中、英文科沒有取得3或以上的成績，因為進不了大學門檻，需要就讀副學士或其他自資院校。他們建議教育局應放寬大學入學門檻，例如4個核心科目最少達2級，而4個核心科目總分不低於10分。<br />\n<br />\n校長會建議，教育局應把適齡組別入讀公費資助大學的百分比，增加至50%，滿足學生升學需求，及追平其他地區如新加坡、上海的比例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1405820-20180708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1405820-20180708.htm&d=%2BQFYoT12wV6bnFPji%2BooSZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=aeb313ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1405820-20180708.htm&h=59586d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1405820-20180708.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又想搞全民大學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb43861125f705d892fafb0027aa63bb209bd987","tid":734099,"uid":45342,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:50:33.000Z","msg":"香港人英文越黎越差<br />\n仲想降低要求？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29311fe55ce84d91f6987ea9e90ea7c480820243","tid":734099,"uid":24140,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"應該降低中文要求<br />\n英文不變"},{"pid":"77a4139b69885e8c6ae0b701a196236b33435b59","tid":734099,"uid":53773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10